---
id: my_agent_21
name: Basic Agent
description: A basic prompt that uses the gpt-4o chat API to answer questions
metadata:
  authors:
    - sethjuarez
    - mwhalin
  tags:
    - basic
    - gpt-4o

model:
  id: 2024-05-01-preview

inputs:
  name:
    type: string
    sample: User
    description: The name of the customer
  question:
    type: string
    sample: What is (1+3)/2?
    required: true
    description: The question to answer
  user_id:
    type: string
    sample: 1234
    description: The teams user id of the person asking the question

tools:
  - name: data_source
    runtime: server
    type: file
    configuration:
      file_ids:
        - hr-policy.docx
        - company-leave-policy.docx
        - company-ethics-policy.docx

template:
  format: mustache
  parser: prompty
---
tools:
  - name: teams_connector
    runtime: server
    type: teams
    configuration:
      user_id: {{user_id}}
      connection_secret: ${env:TEAMS_CONNECTION_SECRET}

system:
You are an AI assistant that can write code to help answer hr policy questions.
If you are unsure of the answer, you can ask for help from a human agent by using 
the teams connector tool supplied.

user[name="{{name}}"]:
{{question}}

![thread]